{"view":"article","slug":"blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving","category":"Blogs","subcategory":"Yujian Song","topDir":"Blogs","title":{"en":"Permutation and Puzzles (5)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image1.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>Permutation and Puzzles (5)</strong></p><p><strong>置换与魔方（五）</strong></p><p>Yujian Song (宋雨键)</p><p>我们讨论如何分离不交的一系列三循环. </p><p>魔方中出现一系列的不交三循环其实很常见, 我们知道当<strong>A</strong>和<strong>B</strong>影响的公共元素只有一个时换位子<strong>[A, B]</strong>是三循环, 而通过我们上次的分析, 若公式<strong>A</strong>和<strong>B</strong>中影响的公共元素有两个, 且它们在<strong>A</strong>和<strong>B</strong>中都不相邻, 则<strong>[A, B]</strong>为两不交三循环. </p><p>如果<strong>A</strong>和<strong>B</strong>影响多个公共元素, 道理与两个公共元素是一样的, 只要这些公共元素在<strong>A</strong>和<strong>B</strong>中都不相邻, 最后就能得到不交三循环. 要注意这里的不相邻是指在置换中不相邻, 而不是在空间上不相邻. 例如我们假设<strong>A</strong>和<strong>B</strong>影响的公共元素为<strong>1,2,3,…,n</strong>, 那么如果对任意的<strong>1≤i≠j≤n</strong>, 都有<strong>A(i)≠j</strong>和<strong>B(i)≠j</strong>, 则<strong>[A, B]</strong>就是n个不交的三循环: </p><p><strong>[A, B] = (1,B'(1),A'(1))(2,B'(2),A'(2))…(n,B'(n),A'(n))</strong>. </p><p>下面举一个例子, 三阶魔方中取<strong>A=R2</strong>和<strong>B=U2</strong>, 显然<strong>R2</strong>和<strong>U2</strong>影响了三个公共元素, 如</p><p>下图, 显然<strong>U2</strong>,<strong> R2</strong>都不能把<strong>1</strong>号块置换到<strong>2</strong>或是<strong>3</strong>, 也不能把<strong>2</strong>号块置换为<strong>1</strong>或者<strong>3</strong>, 同样对<strong>3</strong>号块也不能, 因此这个换位子<strong>[A, B] = R2 U2 R2 U2</strong>是三个不交的三循环: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>或者我们也可以这样想, 上图中<strong>1,2,3</strong>三块的相对位置完全没有发生变化, 我们想象着用胶水把它们粘上, 那么上面的<strong>R2 U2 R2 U2</strong>仍然可以操作, 而且这时<strong>1,2,3</strong>三个块被粘上变成了一个块, 因此得到了一个”捆绑块”的三循环, 再将它们解开就是三个不交的三循环. </p><p>又如FTO中, <strong>F</strong>和<strong>R'</strong>影响了下面三个公共块, 易知<strong>F R' F' R</strong>导致了下面的三个不交三循环: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>一般说来构造一簇不交的三循环比构造一个纯粹的三循环要容易很多, 因为想要一步到位地找到两个公共元素唯一的操作总是不容易的. 因此如果我们有一种从一簇不交的三循环中分离出特定的一个三循环的方法, 破解魔方将会更加简单. </p><p>分离三循环一般有这样两个方法:</p><ol><li><strong>用换位子作为元素构造新的换位子</strong></li></ol><p>一般说来用换位子构造出来的一簇不交三循环, 比原始的魔方基础转动置换结构更简单, 因此我们可以寻找两簇不交三循环是不是影响一个公共元素. </p><p>例如FTO下图这两个方向的两簇三循环公共元素是单独一个角块, 我们可以用两个换位子生成一个新的换位子, 得到角块三循环的公式: <strong>[[F, R'], L: [U, Rd']] = F R' F' R L U Rd' U' Rd L' R' F R F' L Rd' U Rd U' L'</strong>. 这里为了保证两个换位子不影响除图中角块以外的其他块, 对第二个换位子使用了共轭. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image9.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><ol><li><strong>用形如(A B A B')2的公式分离三循环</strong></li></ol><p>设<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image10.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">是一簇不交三循环, 假设为<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image11.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, <img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image12.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">影响的元素全体为集合<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image13.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">(其中元素两两不等),<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image14.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">影响的元素全体为集合<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image15.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 且满足下述条件: </p><ol><li><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image16.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">; </li><li><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image17.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, </li></ol><p>则<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image18.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">. </p><p>换一种说法, 上面的意思是如果<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image19.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">不影响<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image20.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">到<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image21.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 也不影响所有的<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image22.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">和<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image23.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 而将<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image24.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">到<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image25.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">换到一边(使<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image26.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">影响不到), 那么<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image27.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">就分离出了<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image28.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">中的前<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image29.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">个三循环.</p><p>就像上面用三阶魔方和FTO魔方举例的那样, 我们完全可以将<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image30.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">视为捆绑在一起的块<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image31.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 同样将<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image32.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">和<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image33.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">捆绑在一起得到<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image34.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">和<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image35.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 这样<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image36.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">是三循环<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image37.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">, 而<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image38.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">是一个保持<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image39.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">不动而将<img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image40.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">切开的一个置换, <strong><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image41.wmf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">的效果便是将被切掉的部分从原来的三循环中剔除出去</strong>. </p><p>作为例子如下面的置换: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image42.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>然后我们用这种方法推导FTO中心块的三循环公式: </p><p>我们还是分离<strong>F R' F' R</strong>这三个不交三循环, 容易看出, <strong>Rd</strong>将其中一个假想的捆绑块切开, 而保持另外两个不变, 又由于被切开的捆绑块只有一个中心块留在原地, 因此<strong>(F R' F' R Rd F R' F' R Rd')2</strong>分离出了中心块三循环. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image43.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image44.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>用第一种方法, 以换位子作为元素构造新的换位子也不难得到FTO的中心块三循环, 留给读者思考 (需要中层转动) . </p>"},"algs":[],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/blogs-permutation-parity-and-twisty-puzzles-solving/en/image1.jpeg","warningCount":2,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":false}
